256
00:32:56,180 --> 00:32:57,410
CONNOR:
Mike.

257
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:04,370
Dad forgot to give you this.

258
00:33:04,540 --> 00:33:08,140
It's just a reminder for Tony Calvino.
