259
00:33:09,180 --> 00:33:10,740
Are you coming?

260
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:14,500
No, I'm under house arrest for a while.

261
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:19,180
Look, I'm sorry about last night. I am.

262
00:33:19,340 --> 00:33:22,970
I was... Yeah.

263
00:33:23,340 --> 00:33:25,380
All right.

264
00:33:28,580 --> 00:33:30,140
