266
00:33:48,340 --> 00:33:50,620
Yeah, and who are you?

267
00:33:52,620 --> 00:33:53,610
Mike Sullivan.

268
00:33:53,980 --> 00:33:56,450
Yes, sir.

269
00:33:59,260 --> 00:34:00,820
You gonna frisk me?

