285
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:15,140
- Sure.
- Thank you, Mr. Sullivan.

286
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:18,020
Thank you very much.
I appreciate it.

287
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:19,700
(KNOCKING)

288
00:35:21,780 --> 00:35:25,780
Mr. Calvino?
Mr. Calvino, Mike Sullivan's here.

289
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:28,940
- Shit.
- He wants to see you.

290
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:33,780
- Shit. Is he packing?
- Not anymore.

291
00:35:34,060 --> 00:35:35,970
All right.

292
00:35:36,300 --> 00:35:37,740
Show him in.

293
00:35:37,900 --> 00:35:41,940
Hey, hey, hey.
You stick around, okay?

294
00:35:50,540 --> 00:35:51,820
Hey!

295
00:35:51,980 --> 00:35:55,940
How the hell are you?
Things good with the old man?

296
00:35:56,100 --> 00:35:57,220
Yeah.

297
00:35:57,460 --> 00:36:01,900
What brings you here?
Don't imagine it's the pussy.

298
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:07,850
- I have a letter for you from Mr. Rooney.
